cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.NI, cs.CY, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the security and privacy concerns related to mobile devices and their network traffic. It involves the analysis of encrypted TCP/IP packets to identify specific user actions on Android apps. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as social and information networks (cs.SI), network and internet architecture (cs.NI), cybercrime (cs.CY), and multimedia (cs.MM).
